Human Tasks Required:
1. Download the Merriweather Bold font in WOFF2 format from Google Fonts:
   - Visit https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Merriweather
   - Select the Bold (700) weight
   - Download the WOFF2 format
   
2. Place the downloaded Merriweather-Bold.woff2 file in:
   src/web/src/assets/fonts/merriweather/

3. Verify the font file works correctly by:
   - Checking it loads properly in the browser
   - Confirming the @font-face declaration in CSS can access it
   - Testing bold text rendering in the application

4. Ensure proper CORS and caching headers are configured on the web server for .woff2 files